snippet.title: Pink | Pixel Horror Game | No Commentary
snippet.description:
Game: Pink
Find the game here: https://augogames.itch.io/pink
Original creator: AugoGames
Release Date: 2020
Engine: GameMaker
I do NOT own anything on this video, all credit to their respective creators.

It's kind of like an RPG Maker Horror game, but it's not made with RPG Maker, so I used Pixel Horror in the thumbnail instead. That's why I covered it. A very short horror game but nice enough.

My hiatus is not over. I just felt like recording.
